fm: int idist(int x1, int y1, int x2, int y2) {     int dx = x2 - x1;     if (dx < 0) {         dx = -dx;     }      int dy = y2 - y1;     if (dy < 0) {         dy = -dy;     }      int dm = (dx <= dy) ? dx : dy;      return dx + dy - (dm / 2); }
